<div id="block-block-1"
     class="block block-block bottom__about-crs last even">

      
  <div class="content">
    <div class="about__content">
<p>Catholic Relief Services <span style="line-height: 22.3999996185303px;">eases suffering and provides assistance to people in need in more than 100 countries, without regard to race, religion or nationality</span>.</p>
</div>
<div class="about__content"><a href="http://www.caritas.org/" target="_blank"><div class="media media-element-container media-media_original">

  <img height="67" width="67" style="width: 67px; height: 67px;" class="media-image media-element file-media-original caritas" typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://www.crs.org/sites/default/files/caritas_0.png" alt="" title="" /></div></a><a href="http://ncdc.org/" target="_blank"><div class="media media-element-container media-media_original">

  <img height="82" width="57" style="width: 57px; height: 82px;" class="media-image media-element file-media-original ncdc" typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://www.crs.org/sites/default/files/ncdc_0.png" alt="" title="" /></div></a><a href="http://www.usccb.org/" target="_blank"><div class="media media-element-container media-media_original">

  <img height="80" width="80" style="width: 80px; height: 80px;" class="media-image media-element file-media-original usccb" typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://www.crs.org/sites/default/files/usccb_0.png" alt="" title="" /></div></a></div>
<div class="about__content">
<p>We are the official overseas relief and development agency of the <a href="http://www.usccb.org/">United States Conference of Catholic Bishops</a> and a member of <a href="http://www.caritas.org/">Caritas Internationalis</a> and the <a href="http://ncdc.org/">National Catholic Development Conference</a>.</p>
